reviewText: I just love her movies.  SO glad I found this 4 film collection.
cute movie collection, gwyneth is great

I liked the previous reviews so purchased this. Wasn't too happy with the Bounce film as it was somewhat depressing and a disappointment given the great actors but poor plot. Still haven't viewed the last two yet.
Perfect collection!  Very reasonably priced for all that is included.

I bought it for one filmand the other three were extra. Not so bad, but there are some films that have a low quality...but well, it's the way they made the dvd, nothing related with Amazon. Good collection for Gwyneth Paltrow's fan.
Emma was our favorite especially my wife who wanted the 4pack set. They all were good and very entertaining as well as hart warming even to tears.

I loved seeing you offer this collection when I was buying single DVDs...I got all my favorites at a price I could afford!  Delivery was quick, prices were great!  I'll be purchasing again in the near future!  Thank-you
I love the view from the top. The other vintage movies are sleeping potions, you need them to get you to sleep fast.
